  "title": "PLC Engineer | Electrical Control System | Vessels | West",
  "description": "<p>Our client is a <strong>Marine and Offshore Industry.</strong> Due to business needs, they are now recruiting a System Control Engineer to be part of their Team for ongoing transformation projects. They are located in the <strong>West </strong>- easily accessible.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Assist in designing and developing electrical and automation systems for vessels.</li><li>Prepare, interpret, and update electrical drawings, schematics, and wiring diagrams.</li><li>Support PLC programming and configure VFDs, motor controllers, and motion control systems.</li><li>Work with breakers, contactors, and control panels to facilitate system integration.</li><li>Participate in Factory Acceptance Tests (FAT), Site Acceptance Tests (SAT), and vessel commissioning.</li><li>Troubleshoot system issues under the supervision of senior engineers.</li><li>Ensure all designs adhere to class, safety, and quality standards.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Min Diploma in Electrical Engineering, Mechatronics, Automation, or related field.</li><li>Basic experience with PLC programming and electrical troubleshooting.</li><li>Entry-level candidates are welcome to apply. On-the-job training will be provided.</li></ul><p><em>Interested candidates who wish to apply for the advertised position, please click </em><em><strong>APPLY NOW</strong></em><em> or email an updated copy of your resume/cv.</em><br /><em>We regret that only shortlisted candidate will be notified.</em></p><p><em>Email Address: </em><a href=\"mailto:jobs@recruitpedia.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><em>jobs@recruitpedia.sg</em></a></p><p><em>Recruitpedia Pte. Ltd.</em><br /><em>EA License No: 19C9682</em><br /><em>EA Personnel No: R25157233 (Loh Pooi Keng)</em></p>",
